data.description: Custom-built steel-constructed home in a beautiful country setting! UNRESTRICTED 14.5 acre paradise! Surrounded by trees this 5 BD / 4.5 BA home is ready for your recreational adventures or your private oasis! Bamboo hardwood floors, cathedral ceilings, stacked stone see-through fireplace, formal dining, massive granite island in kitchen, office, den, game room, 2-story wrap-a-round covered deck, hardy board siding, his & her master closets, whirlpool tub, walk-in shower, updated primary bath with custom tile shower, new high-end water filtration system/softener, oversized 2 car garage with storage closet, partial home generator, freshly painted lower level, metal barn w/water and power (with septic available), shed & more!
